\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6.2}{\ignorespaces Cost scaling projections: daily and monthly costs as query volume increases from 50 to 2000 queries/day. Left panel shows daily operating cost (dominated by query-proportional LLM inference cost ~\$0.002/query + fixed infrastructure \$0.43/day). Right panel shows monthly cost trajectory from ~\$3.43/month (50 q/day) to ~\$120/month (2000 q/day), well within budget for reasonable production workloads. Linear scaling until free-tier exhaustion; beyond 500k tokens/day, backend fallback incurs marginal cost increase.}}{53}{figure.caption.196}%
